If you want to understand the principles on which international relations are built, watch the Brigade series. Everything is the same, even the vocabulary becomes similar. If you want to understand what is going on in Ukraine, watch the movie Nobody Survived. This is a film about how a gang of thug robbers ran into a psychopathic maniac, and what came of it. If you want to get an idea of ​​what's in store for the common people, check out the trailer for Alien vs. Predator. There is a famous phrase: "Whoever wins, we lose." If you want to understand human psychology, watch a documentary about the life of a flock of baboons. Darwin was right, we definitely evolved from monkeys.